=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#official-resources\">Official resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#community-resources\">Community resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#presentations\">Presentations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#blog-posts\">Blog posts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#addons\">Addons</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"official-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#official-resources\" aria-label=\"official resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Official resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org\">Website</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/docs/basics/introduction/\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/storybookjs\">GitHub organization</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/use-cases/\">Use cases</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/team/\">Team</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community-resources\" aria-label=\"community resources permalink\" class=\"anchor bef